author: jukka
msg: JCR-2453: Break the spi2dav dependency to jcr-server
Reduce the impact of the jcr-server dependency by excluding the unused transitive dependencies.

The commons-httpclient dependency is already included as a transitive dependency through jackrabbit-webdav, so it's best not to declare it here. This avoids having to deal with the troublesome commons-logging stuff.
